    ("Chemistry", "Aldehydes, Ketones and Carboxylic Acids", "What is the product of the reductive ozonolysis of but-2-ene?", "Two molecules of ethanal (acetaldehyde).", "MODERATE"),
    ("Chemistry", "Aldehydes, Ketones and Carboxylic Acids", "What product is formed when propyne is hydrated in the presence of Hg2+ and H2SO4 at 333 K?", "Propanone (acetone).", "MODERATE"),
